explanations.reason: The paper focuses on hepatitis B virus (HBV) vaccination coverage among people who inject drugs (PWID) in Sydney, Australia. It examines demographic, drug use, and HBV risk factors using multinomial logistic regression. The study does not involve any machine learning techniques, neural networks, or related methodologies mentioned in the provided keywords. The analysis is purely statistical and epidemiological in nature, without any application of advanced computational or AI-based methods.
